author: KLOKRIECHER
title: LEGO Gear (CD/DVDs) - BIONICLE 3: Web Of Shadows DVD Review
review:
This movie is the last BIONICLE movie LEGO ever made. After the Toa Metru has been changed into the Toa Hordika the toa and the rahaga have to find the mighty Keetongou. This creature is the only one who is able to stop the monster in the inside of the Toa Hordika...

Pros

  • Great story
  • Graphics are awsome

Cons

  • None

Summary

All in all it's a great set to get and I would HIGHLY recommend you to get this. You can find this set on eBay, BrickLink and Amazon for sure.
